</paragraph>
<paragraph id="350E57DAE358B75B19A0DC2F34A0F77A" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736">
<emphasis id="B9DBAD81B054FB54F751BC330782B2A4" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736">
Distribution in 
<normalizedToken id="B488DDBE52A1AB28F7BFFF35782AD78E" originalValue="Paraíba">Paraiba</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
: Cabo Branco Beach (
<bibRefCitation id="D85E0B2FB0126DF49E0435796135B84A" author="Gondim, Anne Isabelley" journalOrPublisher="Biota Neotropica" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736" pagination="151 - 159" refId="B6422128" refString="Gondim, Anne Isabelley, Lacouth, Patricia, Alonso, Carmen, Manso, Cynthia Lara de Castro, 2008. Echinodermata from Cabo Branco Beach, Joao Pessoa, Paraiba, Brazil. Biota Neotropica 8 (2): 151 - 159" title="Echinodermata from Cabo Branco Beach, Joao Pessoa, Paraiba, Brazil" volume="8" year="2008">Gondim et al. 2008</bibRefCitation>
), Seixas Beach (
<bibRefCitation id="412EA66D103129FFF27B50552ACFCB8A" author="Prata, Jessica" journalOrPublisher="Biota Neotropica" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736" pagination=": e 20170363" refId="B6423131" refString="Prata, Jessica, Costa, Dimitri Araujo, Manso, Cynthia Lara Castro, Crispim, Maria Cristina, Christoffersen, Martin Lindsey, 2017. Echinodermata associated to rhodoliths from Seixas Beach, State of Paraiba, Northeast Brazil. Biota Neotropica 17 (3): e20170363" title="Echinodermata associated to rhodoliths from Seixas Beach, State of Paraiba, Northeast Brazil" volume="17" year="2017">Prata et al. 2017</bibRefCitation>
) and Miramar Beach (
<emphasis id="0CDEE5184581A83E2EDE0C41C16D2257" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736">New record</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D392DAC857C26F2AB2A6E1F754DADC71" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736" type="notes">
<paragraph id="81209E0E4C19625FF28460BD6EADDA38" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="567529D2880B81FD199B3F731D3654A1" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736">Found on the rhodoliths surface.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3421E99CC3E6FE710C8808178ED5AFDA" pageId="0" pageNumber="62736">
